Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.85,0:21:59.12,ENJP,NTP,0,0,0,,真っ直ぐに歩いてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.78,0:22:07.20,ENJP,NTP,0,0,0,,不器用なこの心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.03,0:22:21.72,ENJP,NTP,0,0,0,,偽りないその目に映る暖かい光りを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.72,0:22:26.77,ENJP,NTP,0,0,0,,溢れる希望の中で今僕ら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.04,0:22:32.22,ENJP,NTP,0,0,0,,どれだけの愛に出逢えるのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.22,0:22:39.03,ENJP,NTP,0,0,0,,同じ時を今生きている愛すると
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.34,0:22:44.37,ENJP,NTP,0,0,0,,思う喜び に触れて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.85,0:21:59.12,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,筆直地一路走來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.78,0:22:07.20,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我這顆笨拙的心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.03,0:22:21.72,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,感受著你的真誠雙眼所發出的溫暖光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.72,0:22:26.77,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,沐浴在滿溢而出的希望中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.04,0:22:32.22,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我們究竟能遇見多深沉的愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.22,0:22:39.03,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,一起活在當下 愛在此時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.34,0:22:44.37,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,如此想來 不禁欣喜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.89,0:00:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫剛田猛男 是個高一學生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.89,0:00:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時值夏季 藍藍的天空 大大的太陽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.51,0:00:11.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草木和蟲子全都活力滿滿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.35,0:00:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 猛男同學 蒲公英哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.09,0:00:18.56,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}山丘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.54,0:00:18.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:22.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白車軸草哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.27,0:00:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學 像王子一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.12,0:00:31.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.04,0:02:06.63,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,475)\fad(0,800)}我的山
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.40,0:02:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和 今天無論發生什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.45,0:02:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都會一直陪在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:12.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用老放在心上的說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是個非常棒的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.47,0:02:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我超級滿足的說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.90,0:02:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.81,0:02:19.78,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.03,0:02:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天 我和大和為了補過生日出來野餐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.49,0:02:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和 你的包好像很重
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.86,0:02:30.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我吧 我幫你拿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.38,0:02:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.36,0:02:34.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裡面都放了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.11,0:02:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 有便當還有便當還有水壺之類的..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.04,0:02:41.75,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}便當 水果 水壺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.44,0:02:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡面全是便當嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.33,0:02:45.68,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}點心 毛巾 野餐墊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.58,0:02:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有點心 毛巾 野餐墊 垃圾袋..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.77,0:02:50.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備這麼多一定很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.74,0:02:52.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不是做太多了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.38,0:02:54.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹勁一來就擋不住呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.42,0:02:57.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學能吃完嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.13,0:03:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和 胸針很適合你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.77,0:03:08.24,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}到山頂還有2公里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.11,0:03:07.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從這往右呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.66,0:03:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 天氣真不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 大和
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.96,0:03:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你累了嗎？要休息一下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.31,0:03:23.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.66,0:03:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不累啦 我還蠻有體力的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:30.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是對不起哦 我走得有點慢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:34.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次與其說野餐 其實是登山嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可能失誤了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.05,0:03:39.52,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}這次沒有問砂川的意見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對不起 一開心就哼起歌了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.97,0:03:51.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好難為情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.85,0:03:54.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和 我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.18,0:03:59.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了 好舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在山上吃的便當一定會很好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:04.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.75,0:04:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走起路來就好熱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.20,0:04:10.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.03,0:04:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學送我的胸針
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.14,0:04:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.51,0:04:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和 大和的便當 花冠..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.26,0:05:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學 你沒事吧？沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.92,0:05:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒事 便當也完好無損哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 靠自己爬上去是行不通的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得趕緊呼救
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.69,0:05:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學 沒信號
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.18,0:05:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.16,0:05:22.17,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}野餐遇險？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:25.04,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}此時 大和的朋友們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.64,0:05:25.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 今天凜子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.58,0:05:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說和猛男同學去野餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,0:05:30.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野餐啊 很適合那一對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.08,0:05:32.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊 男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.67,0:05:34.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交往已經差不多2個月了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砂川同學雖然很帥 但是拿他沒轍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.80,0:05:39.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全說不上話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而凜子的男朋友要說帥嘛..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.63,0:05:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該怎麼形容才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.05,0:05:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男子漢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.92,0:05:50.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 男子漢..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.87,0:05:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與其說帥..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.82,0:05:56.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在凜子眼中好像比砂川同學還帥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:05:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:05:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看得出來看得出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:01.96,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}此時 剛田家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.23,0:06:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子他媽 身體沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:06.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 沒事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.44,0:06:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子他媽 猛男去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.73,0:06:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來好像沒看到他人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.71,0:06:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊讓開一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.17,0:06:16.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是和阿誠在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到時候就回來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:22.23,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}此時 砂川
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.26,0:06:29.73,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}第一本...第二本...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.21,0:06:36.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四周沒有人路過的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:39.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.43,0:06:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我的錯..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:43.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:44.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總有辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.24,0:06:50.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這等一下 我去上面看看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.48,0:06:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？上面？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.20,0:06:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學 小心一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.44,0:07:02.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要抓住了樹 就沒有掉下去過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.50,0:07:06.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過去的事也沒什麼好說的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.16,0:07:08.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我該做的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是把大和毫髮無傷的送回家中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.26,0:07:16.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.52,0:07:21.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題 大和 我們回得去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.08,0:07:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠輕微地聽到汽車聲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.36,0:07:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊一定有道路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.52,0:07:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？猛男同學好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是很遠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到街上可能要到明天了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.95,0:07:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒..那麼..一整晚要兩人獨處..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.71,0:07:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.42,0:07:45.02,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}一整晚..兩人獨處..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.74,0:07:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會很不安呢 大和
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:58.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都不用擔心 都交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先朝南一直走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.73,0:08:07.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊是南邊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:09.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和跟緊我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.75,0:08:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢走就好 趁太陽沒下山多走些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.31,0:08:17.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為很容易跟丟 所以就抓住我的衣角吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.22,0:08:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學 吃便當吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.71,0:08:50.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 大和 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.49,0:08:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多吃一點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:53.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曉得了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.94,0:08:54.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.63,0:08:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:08:59.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎？太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.25,0:09:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對料理沒那麼擅長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.95,0:09:07.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在外面吃飯更添風味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:11.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.08,0:09:13.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.18,0:09:15.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？這樣就夠了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.96,0:09:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一半留到晚上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 趁太陽下山前再努力一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.22,0:09:27.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.85,0:09:32.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和 你很不安呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.66,0:09:34.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想讓你安下心來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.98,0:09:46.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始看不清腳下了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.68,0:09:48.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就在這裡野宿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.37,0:09:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和在這裡睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.20,0:10:03.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野宿..和猛男同學兩個人一起..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.19,0:10:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題的 我就在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:12.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.00,0:10:17.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有蚊子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.88,0:10:26.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不會讓你們對大和下口
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.28,0:10:35.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和 手機還是接不通嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:37.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.21,0:10:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是沒信號
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.62,0:10:43.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 大家一定都很擔心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:44.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.01,0:10:49.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說換成那個待機畫面 就能交上男朋友哦..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.91,0:10:52.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺好假哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.41,0:10:55.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒騙你們啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰啊？喂喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.69,0:10:57.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 凜子的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:10:59.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.14,0:11:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是 誒？凜子沒回家？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之後發給你們哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.56,0:11:06.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她問有沒有和我們在一起..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.84,0:11:10.60,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(490,140)}因為約會而回不去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.09,0:11:10.60,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,140)}=
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.34,0:11:10.60,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,140)}過夜了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.61,0:11:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在..在啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.29,0:11:14.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凜子在我家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.16,0:11:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他朋友也都在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.14,0:11:17.23,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}朋友的謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.39,0:11:18.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？現在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.66,0:11:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個..她在洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.93,0:11:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 請放心 是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.72,0:11:29.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是 大家今天也都會住下 是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:30.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 快點給凜子打電話 電話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.90,0:11:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟她說已經幫她做好偽證了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.37,0:11:41.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將為您接通電話錄音服務
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:43.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 手機打不通 怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發信息去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:48.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們倆去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.50,0:11:49.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砂川同學的話應該知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:51.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人知道他的電話號碼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.17,0:11:54.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:56.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菜菜子醬？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.37,0:11:58.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼什麼 好開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.31,0:12:01.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然特地在假日打電話找我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天我超級空的 一起去玩..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.78,0:12:06.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 你知道凜子和他男朋友去哪了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.71,0:12:07.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野餐之後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:09.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？野餐？什麼什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.06,0:12:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事了 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.31,0:12:15.28,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}另一方面 此時的剛田家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.64,0:12:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子他媽 身體沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.62,0:12:18.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.72,0:12:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男 還沒有回來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.29,0:12:23.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用擔心不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.14,0:12:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到時候就會回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.00,0:12:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:29.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚餐 留著給他明天當早餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.16,0:12:31.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保鮮膜保鮮膜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.55,0:12:33.27,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}此時的砂川
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:37.85,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}第三本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝招待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.81,0:12:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山裡的夜晚 黑乎乎的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.87,0:12:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學 請問..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.08,0:12:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以..牽著手嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.18,0:12:58.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.66,0:13:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼東西過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:28.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學 剛才那個是什麼？熊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:31.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事 只是野豬而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.69,0:13:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 野..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的 我就在這
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.53,0:13:40.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:43.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和 聲音好像很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.48,0:13:45.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.40,0:13:48.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是熊 我也打敗給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定保護好你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:57.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月亮變亮了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.59,0:14:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.95,0:14:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼亮的話 大和也會安心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.98,0:14:06.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.21,0:14:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了一天你也累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躺下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.61,0:14:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 同床共枕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.29,0:14:24.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.44,0:14:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:29.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星星很漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.19,0:14:35.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為四周很暗 所以能看到很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.95,0:14:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 就像天文館一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:47.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和沒問題吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:50.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.89,0:14:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會不安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:54.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.46,0:14:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然猛男同學一直問我有沒有事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.01,0:14:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我真的沒事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.97,0:15:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.93,0:15:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.83,0:15:03.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.94,0:15:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:15.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算一生都要在這深山裡兩人生活我也覺得很幸福哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.93,0:15:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛..猛男同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:38.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到猛男同學的睡臉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 猛男同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.77,0:15:50.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都因為我 讓你累壞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就我一個人在那瞎興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:56.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學..喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.41,0:15:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.10,0:16:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.39,0:16:57.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到她睡覺的樣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.09,0:17:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.61,0:17:09.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.67,0:17:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.03,0:17:18.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學的身邊來了好多小動物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.17,0:17:23.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和猛男同學在一起就很安心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.77,0:17:25.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.43,0:17:29.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是道路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和 沒受傷吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.02,0:17:48.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 沒事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.02,0:17:49.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好癢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.99,0:17:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.43,0:17:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒能完全保護到位啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.70,0:17:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 猛男同學被叮了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.23,0:18:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從以前就是吸引蚊子的體質
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.46,0:18:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我引走了一隻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.42,0:18:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以讓猛男同學受的傷少了一處呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.41,0:18:10.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:13.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和 我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.71,0:18:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 必須給家裡打個電話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？菜菜子發消息來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凜子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:27.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經幫你跟家裡說好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.84,0:18:30.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天一定要來我家報告全過程
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.39,0:18:31.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.22,0:18:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我去菜菜子家裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.20,0:18:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 幫我跟她問好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.38,0:18:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.31,0:18:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為一直跟猛男同學待在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.98,0:18:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以分別的時候有點寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.10,0:19:00.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見哦 猛男同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.34,0:19:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和 我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.91,0:19:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凜子？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.67,0:19:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切 喂喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.99,0:19:22.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 昨天的電話讓我有點在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.95,0:19:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男和凜子醬發生什麼事了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:27.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與其說發生了什麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.47,0:19:29.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凜子來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.74,0:19:31.12,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼什麼 告訴我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.55,0:19:31.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等得人家都沒睡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.74,0:19:34.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 如何啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.56,0:19:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還以為..要死了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.46,0:19:42.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒誒誒 不知羞恥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:42.69,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}昨夜很歡愉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.06,0:19:44.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.31,0:19:45.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼難以啟齒的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.73,0:19:46.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事啦 我不會亂說..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.34,0:19:48.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快 詳細招來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:52.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 太刺激了還以為心臟都壞掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.53,0:19:54.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這是我的第一次..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.06,0:19:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且一直在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.31,0:19:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 外面？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.68,0:20:02.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 因為是猛男同學所以很安心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然有野豬跑出來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.34,0:20:07.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我睡得很沉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.55,0:20:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說凜子 你全身髒兮兮的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.26,0:20:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底遇上了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是遇了點險啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.12,0:20:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.24,0:20:16.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.41,0:20:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老媽 身體沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.35,0:20:21.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.38,0:20:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.40,0:20:25.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛 山裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:26.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你擔心了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.08,0:20:27.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.03,0:20:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.11,0:20:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能平安回來太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.71,0:20:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明猛男同學為了我那麼拼命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.58,0:20:40.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我卻一個人在那瞎興奮 對不起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然跟猛男同學一直待在一塊讓我心跳得好快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.29,0:20:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是真的很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:48.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:20:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:21:01.97,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}還在睡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.77,0:21:00.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教我用繪文字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.25,0:21:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對大和的心情無法用語言表達
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.73,0:21:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 什麼樣的心情？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.05,0:21:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:16.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bang!Dong!Wang!Kang!..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.21,0:21:18.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.80,0:21:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男 我覺得你的心情用繪文字也不能表達
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.29,0:21:30.01,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}From 猛男同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.29,0:21:30.01,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}To 大和凜子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.29,0:21:30.01,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}主題 re：沒事太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.29,0:21:30.01,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.94,0:21:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡你到不行 大和
